OL,3,CJobs at risk at Plymouth Argyle in
OL,4,Cclub 'restructure'
OL,6,FA redundancy process is ongoing at
OL,7,FPlymouth Argyle, ITV News understands.
OL,9,FA consultation has begun on a
OL,10,Frestructure of operations at the
OL,11,Ffootball club, as it deals with
OL,12,Fongoing financial pressures.
OL,14,FAccording to Plymouth Argyle, this
OL,15,Fdecision has been made after the
OL,16,Freturn to League One and wider
OL,17,Finflation has resulted in "significant
OL,18,Ffinancial losses".
