OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1773087075
OL,3,CJobs at risk at Plymouth Argyle in
OL,4,Cclub 'restructure'
OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "The club can
OL,7,Fconfirm it has proposed to staff a
OL,8,Frestructure of its operations.
OL,10,F"In the past four years, the club has
OL,11,Fprogressed in many areas. However, the
OL,12,Freturn to League One, coupled with
OL,13,Fwider inflationary pressures, has
OL,14,Fresulted in the club incurring
OL,15,Fsignificant financial losses.
OL,17,F"This is being proposed in order to
OL,18,Faddress significant financial
OL,19,Fpressures, and to assist the club in
OL,20,Ftrying to ensure long-term
OL,21,Fsustainability."
OL,26,@rD@AOUyD@AOU}D@PO]
