OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1773087075
OL,3,CJobs at risk at Plymouth Argyle in
OL,4,Cclub 'restructure'
OL,6,FThe consultation process comes off the
OL,7,Fback of the club's relegation to
OL,8,FLeague One from the Championship last
OL,9,Fseason.
OL,11,FArgyle had been promoted to the second
OL,12,Ftier under Steve Schumacher in 2023.
OL,13,FThey maintained their league status
OL,14,Fbut dropped back to the third tier
OL,15,Funder the management of Wayne Rooney
OL,16,Fand Miron Muslic.
OL,18,FThere has been no confirmation of how
OL,19,Fmany roles may be affected at this
OL,20,Fstage.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
